<div style="text-align: center; padding: 40px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h1>🔒 Parental Consent Required</h1>
  
  <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3>Hi <%= current_user.email %>!</h3>
    <p>You are <strong><%= current_user.age %> years old</strong>, which means you need parental consent to access this application.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h4>What happens next?</h4>
    <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 10px 0;">
      <li>An administrator will review your registration</li>
      <li>Your parent/guardian will be contacted for consent</li>
      <li>Once approved, you'll have full access to the application</li>
      <li>You'll receive an email notification when approved</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h4>📋 Account Status</h4>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= current_user.email %></p>
    <p><strong>Age:</strong> <%= current_user.age %> years old</p>
    <p><strong>Registration Date:</strong> <%= current_user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
    <p><strong>Parental Consent:</strong> 
      <span style="color: #d32f2f; font-weight: bold;">⏳ Pending Approval</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
      Questions? Contact support or ask your parent/guardian to reach out to us.
    </p>
    
    <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, data: { "turbo-method": :delete }, 
        style: "display: inline-block; background: #1976d2; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 10px;" %>
  </div>
</div>
